Aoora, who has released a song "Blue Ocean" on the begining of 2018, has returned "Harder".
The new song "Harder" is a classic funky pop genre with vintage guitar riffs and synthesizer loop. It features Japanese artist B.E., popular in Asia model Eiji and musically talented rapper $milli. Together they brought music quality to the next level. 
This album, funded by fans from all over the world, sends a positive message to always live happily and never lose our passion. It will entertain music fans this summer.
